    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It still looks great and drives even better! I've taken good care of it, and I'm looking for a new owner who will appreciate it just as much as I have. It's the perfect mix of reliable and stylish\u2014ready to hit the road whenever you are! Drop me a message if you'd like to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
