    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability, having been kept in consistent, smoke-free condition. The exterior paint maintains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well\u2014standard for its age but otherwise very clean. Inside, the cabin is inviting; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronic components, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It comes with a full service portfolio, including a brand-new set of all-season tires and a recent fluid flush. This is a well-sorted, dependable car ready for its next owner to drive home with peace of mind.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
