    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs super smoothly, and is ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s perfect if you want something dependable and comfortable without that brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
